headline: ELAHERE® (mirvetuximab soravtansine-gynx) Shows Consistent Survival Benefit in Long-Term Analysis for Certain Ovarian Cancer Patients
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced the final analysis of the confirmatory Phase 3 MIRASOL trial evaluating the efficacy and safety of ELAHERE® (mirvetuximab soravtansine-gynx) in women with folate receptor alpha (FRα)-positive platinum-resistant ovarian cancer (PROC) compared to chemotherapy.
